Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.18,0:00:12.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NThat was the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.39,0:00:14.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.68,0:00:17.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I've never\Ntold anyone how I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:19.60,Main,,0,0,0,,You were the first person
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.69,0:00:22.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I've ever been\Ncompletely honest with.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.73,0:00:25.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:30.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NThank you for that, Hanayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.42,0:02:11.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru, dear,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.97,0:02:13.72,Main,,0,0,0,,that's sweet of you, but you're\Ngoing to be late for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:16.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.59,0:02:18.35,Main,,0,0,0,,You get going,\NI'll take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.43,0:02:20.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhh, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:22.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:26.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:39.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:42.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA yawns]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:44.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Oh, good morning, Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.04,0:02:47.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tama. School time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.21,0:02:49.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Can't I sleep just\Nanother five minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.54,0:02:52.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess, but you're\Ncoming with either way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:14.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.07,0:03:17.91,Main,,0,0,0,,U-Um, Yuzuki... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:22.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] I'm takin' off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:26.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[LANDLADY]\NAll alone today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:28.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Where's your sister?\NShouldn't you two be together?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.67,0:03:31.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?! The heck's\Nthat supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.79,0:03:33.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[LANDLADY] Ah, kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:45.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 9A] Akira's still missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:47.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:48.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 9B] Yeah, they\Ninterviewed a girl
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:49.69,Main,,0,0,0,,from her school in that article.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:51.44,Main,,0,0,0,,It's like she just disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:53.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Nobody's seen her\Nfor almost a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:05.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NYou're gonna miss the train. Ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:06.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[ANNOUNCER]\NNow departing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:25.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:29.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] We were getting\Nalong so well, but now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:30.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] God, I hate this--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:32.69,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't be friends anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:34.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] No, we can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:36.07,Main,,0,0,0,,She's right. 'Cause...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:39.28,Main,,0,0,0,,...I refuse to have\Nany more battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:42.91,Main,,0,0,0,,But Yuzuki won't stop battling\Nuntil her wish comes true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:46.54,Main,,0,0,0,,No matter how many people\Nshe hurts in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:51.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] But I... I\Ncan't live like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:57.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[students murmuring]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:58.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOY 9A] You serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:00.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOY 9B] Pretty freaky, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:01.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 9C] The twins?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:04.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 9D] Yeah, can you\Nbelieve they're a couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:06.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOY 9C]\NLike... incest for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:08.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 9E] No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:11.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOY 9D]\NWow, so the rumors are true?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:13.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOY 9E] Oh, you think\Nthey've already done it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:14.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOY 9D] Duh, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:16.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOY 9E] Aw, barf!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:18.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 6B]\NDon't blame yourself, Honoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:19.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 6A] There's no way\Nyou could have known
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:21.03,Main,,0,0,0,,he was like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:22.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 6B] And I used\Nto think he was cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:24.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 6A] He's just gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:26.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:31.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I assume you're the one\Nresponsible for all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:33.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 6B]\NIt's not her fault, jackass!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:34.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, people wouldn't talk
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:36.50,Main,,0,0,0,,if you and your\Nsister acted normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:38.13,Main,,0,0,0,,No, jerk,\NI didn't do a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:40.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I just told a few friends\Nwhat you said to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.80,Main,,0,0,0,,You know, how upset you got\Nwhen you heard the rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:45.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 6B] Honoka was worried\Nabout you, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:47.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I really wasn't trying\Nto start anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:49.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Although, your sister does\Nact kind of weird sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.02,0:05:52.27,Main,,0,0,0,,You know, forget you. I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:54.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Nobody talks bad\Nabout my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:55.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[HONOKA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:57.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't act like I'm some\Nkinda villain! So rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.07,0:05:59.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 6B] Geez, you're horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:01.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 6A] Guh, no wonder\Npeople are saying
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:02.70,Main,,0,0,0,,he and his\Nsister are an item!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:03.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 9F] Apologize to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:05.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 9G] What a weirdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:07.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 9H]\NYou make my skin crawl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.16,0:06:08.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOY 9F] Yeah, with her brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:09.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOY 9G] Aw, nasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.45,0:06:11.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOY 9H] Too bad.\NI thought she was hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.26,0:06:25.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO (Y)] There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:29.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:31.39,Main,,0,0,0,,So I heard you've\Nbeen telling people
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:33.77,Main,,0,0,0,,not to talk about me.\NIs that for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:35.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:38.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO (Y)]\NThat's sweet of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:40.61,Main,,0,0,0,,but it's not\Nreally necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:43.15,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not gossip if it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.24,0:06:45.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Wait a minute,\Nwhat do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:47.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:49.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:50.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha--?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:54.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I've been in love with you\Never since we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:57.25,Main,,0,0,0,,But I never told you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:07:00.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to scare you\Noff, but I've felt this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:02.84,Main,,0,0,0,,...my entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:04.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:06.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[FRIEND A] You've got a crush on\Nthat cute boy Goto, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:08.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[FRIEND B]\NHeh! Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:10.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[FRIEND C]\NAnd you, Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:11.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:13.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO (Y)] While my friends\Nwere always chatting about
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:16.10,Main,,0,0,0,,what boy they had\Na crush on that week...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:18.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[FRIEND 9C]\NC'mon, spill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.23,0:07:19.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:21.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[FRIEND 9A] Everyone said who\Nthey liked! Now it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:22.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[FRIEND 9B]\NWho's your secret crush?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:27.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh... Sorry, but I don't have\None. At least not right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:29.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[FRIEND 9C]\NLiar-liar, pants on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:31.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I'm just not really\Ninto any of the guys
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:32.74,Main,,0,0,0,,in our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:33.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[FRIEND 9B]\NYou're so lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:35.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:36.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[FRIEND 9A]\NTell the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:38.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I am, doofus!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:41.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO (Y)] I couldn't tell\Nanyone how I really felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:43.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[FRIEND 9D]\NSo, um... your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:44.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:46.72,Main,,0,0,0,,...if there's a girl he likes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:49.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Um, well,\Nto tell the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.47,0:07:52.64,Main,,0,0,0,,he's always talking about\Nhow girls are gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:54.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Even when he's watching TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.35,0:07:56.48,Main,,0,0,0,,If like, a kissing\Nscene comes on,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:58.14,Main,,0,0,0,,he always changes the channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.23,0:08:01.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO (Y)]\NI lied to all my friends, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:03.40,Main,,0,0,0,,...I lied to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:05.53,Main,,0,0,0,,The one I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:06.86,Main,,0,0,0,,For the longest time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:09.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought maybe it was\Nbest to keep it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:14.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.37,0:08:16.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you really live like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:18.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:21.79,Main,,0,0,0,,But no matter what, I will\Nstill love Kazuki forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:24.13,Main,,0,0,0,,And it doesn't matter\Nif he finds a girlfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:27.42,Main,,0,0,0,,or gets married,\Nor even if he has kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:30.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll just keep living this\Nlie for the rest of my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:32.01,Main,,0,0,0,,'til I'm old and alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:36.02,Main,,0,0,0,,If this is the only way I can\Nlove him, so be it, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:38.64,Main,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:40.48,Main,,0,0,0,,One day...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:45.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] A card game?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:47.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Yeah, it's pretty fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:51.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:54.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hey, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:55.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:00.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO]\NYou must be my Selector!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:02.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:05.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] My name's\NHanayo. Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:08.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa, that card\Njust talked to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:10.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, the card did what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:13.47,Main,,0,0,0,,It talked. You mean,\Nyou didn't hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:14.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not craz--!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:15.68,Main,,0,0,0,,He can't hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.76,0:09:17.64,Main,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact,\Nthe only ones who can
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:19.43,Main,,0,0,0,,are Selectors like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:21.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, but what have\NI been selected for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:25.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] My wish...\Ncan come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:27.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.36,0:09:30.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Whether you believe that or not,\Nthough, is entirely up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:34.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO]\NYou do have a wish, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:41.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm stuck inside a card.\NYour secret is safe with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:44.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I... love...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:45.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:49.30,Main,,0,0,0,,...Kazuki, I... love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:51.22,Main,,0,0,0,,O-kay. So, who?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:53.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait, you mean your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:04.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Yes, I love\Nhim. I love Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:06.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I love Kazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:08.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I love my brother, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:11.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:13.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I love him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:18.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I know. I know it's not right.\NAnd... I know it's not normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:20.83,Main,,0,0,0,,But I still want\Nto be with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:24.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to spend the\Nrest of my life with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:25.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I want more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:29.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to be\NKazuki's girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:35.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] All right.\NLet's make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:37.93,Main,,0,0,0,,And we'll do it... together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:47.19,Main,,0,0,0,,So, then...\NYour wish was for...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:52.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO (Y)] You once called\Nmy strategy straightforward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:54.61,Main,,0,0,0,,That's how I have\Nto be in life, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:56.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I have to be\Nstraightforward with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:10:59.08,Main,,0,0,0,,The same way I was with Hanayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:03.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NThat was the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:05.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:07.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I've never\Ntold anyone how I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.38,0:11:09.34,Main,,0,0,0,,You were the\Nvery first person...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:11.63,Main,,0,0,0,,...I've ever been\Ncompletely honest with.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:15.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:18.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you for that, Hanayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:25.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't care what it\Nwould take to accomplish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:27.81,Main,,0,0,0,,If there was any chance\Nof being with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:30.52,Main,,0,0,0,,even if it meant me\Ngetting hurt or dying...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.61,0:11:32.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd take it because I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:36.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you feel the same about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:45.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:12:01.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOY 9I] Kazuki? No, he\Nhasn't come back from lunch yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.18,0:12:02.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:04.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 6A] O-M-G! Would\Nyou look who's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:06.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Ew, it's the "brother-lover!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:07.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 9G] That\Nis so skeevy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.73,0:12:09.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRLS giggle maliciously]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:12.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[trains clattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:18.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] A wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:20.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[trains clattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:22.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] One that\Nyou want so badly
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:27.79,Main,,0,0,0,,that you're willing to hurt\Nyourself... or someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:29.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Next time we meet,\NI'll be a new me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:31.58,Main,,0,0,0,,No more regrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.67,0:12:35.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll finally be Kazuki's\Ngirlfriend for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:38.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I tried to\Nstop her, but I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:40.68,Main,,0,0,0,,She didn't care what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:58.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I guess, since I don't\Nhave a wish, I can't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:13:00.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] But it is\Nthe nature of battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.95,0:13:02.95,Main,,0,0,0,,And our nature as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:04.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Both mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:06.29,Main,,0,0,0,,...and yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:11.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not... like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:12.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:13.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:18.47,Main,,0,0,0,,You're feeling sad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:19.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:21.93,Main,,0,0,0,,You know. 'Cause you\Nand Yuzuki and Hitoe
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.01,0:13:25.30,Main,,0,0,0,,were all friends,\Nbut now you're not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:27.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama will still be\Nyour friend, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:29.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:33.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, even if we don't get\Nto battle, we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:35.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:36.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:40.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I like to battle\Nso much, but... you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:43.62,Main,,0,0,0,,So, I'll just stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:46.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Tama. You rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:48.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:50.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:51.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.59,0:13:58.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:01.05,Main,,0,0,0,,What the--? Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:03.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, does this\Nmean you're all better now
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:04.59,Main,,0,0,0,,and you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.68,0:14:05.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:08.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Look, Hitoe has an LRIG!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:12.27,Main,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:13.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] You...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:15.98,Main,,0,0,0,,You're a Selector, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:18.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Please let me challenge\Nyou to a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:19.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha--?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:25.28,Main,,0,0,0,,No. How are you\Na Selector again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:27.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Battle me. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:29.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Just say yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:31.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:34.08,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.67,0:14:37.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Look, I'm real sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:40.50,Main,,0,0,0,,But I've decided not\Nto battle people ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:41.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.80,0:14:44.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Then why are you still\Nkeeping Tama around?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.13,0:14:45.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:46.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NGuess I can't blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:49.85,Main,,0,0,0,,You two are\Npractically best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:50.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:52.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Speaking of friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:54.94,Main,,0,0,0,,can't you do a favor for\Ntwo of your former ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:56.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Just for old times' sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:15:00.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on! Where are you? Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:03.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:04.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:11.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:15.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:17.25,Main,,0,0,0,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:20.59,Main,,0,0,0,,You're an LRIG?\NThis can't be real.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:22.17,Main,,0,0,0,,It's nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:24.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.13,0:15:25.38,Main,,0,0,0,,That can't be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:28.55,Main,,0,0,0,,It's me all right.\NHere, let me prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:31.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:32.81,Main,,0,0,0,,That scrunchie, it's--!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:36.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the one I bought\Nwith you two that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:38.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Guess the three of us\Ncan't stay apart, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:41.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki, what... happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:43.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] S'pose I owe\Nyou an explanation,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:45.07,Main,,0,0,0,,and I'll be happy\Nto give you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:50.41,Main,,0,0,0,,If you agree... to\Na battle with Hitoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:52.87,Main,,0,0,0,,And risk hurting her?\NThere's no freaking way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:55.29,Main,,0,0,0,,You'd be doing\Nit to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:57.37,Main,,0,0,0,,So her wish\Ncan be granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:59.75,Main,,0,0,0,,And so mine can, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:02.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] I need to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:04.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Ruko... Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:07.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NIf it's for my friends, I--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:25.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:29.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:31.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE & RUKO] Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:50.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn it all. I hate this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:58.18,Main,,0,0,0,,'Kay! Grow, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.27,0:16:59.69,Main,,0,0,0,,On it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:03.90,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, Yuzuki! Now\Nyou tell me what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.24,0:17:11.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, for starters,\NI won my final battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:13.16,Main,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:16.24,Main,,0,0,0,,At long last\Nmy wish came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.33,0:17:18.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Since you've made\Nyour decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:21.46,Main,,0,0,0,,let us join together\Nfor one final attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.97,0:17:33.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, the oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.47,0:17:34.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you remember it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.89,0:17:35.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:36.77,Main,,0,0,0,,It's, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:38.27,Main,,0,0,0,,"I accept..."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.35,0:17:40.23,Main,,0,0,0,,"...the laws of the Selector."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.31,0:17:42.69,Main,,0,0,0,,"I accept the laws\Nof the Selector".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:43.77,Main,,0,0,0,,And, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:45.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\N"And upon this sacred oath,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.11,0:17:47.44,Main,,0,0,0,,a new Eternal Girl\Nshall be born!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:50.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH] Adamasphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:15.14,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:18.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Then does that mean\Nyou're not the only Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:24.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:25.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:27.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] So Hanayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:28.78,Main,,0,0,0,,...became you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.86,0:18:31.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Obviously that wasn't\Nwhat I was expecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:33.28,Main,,0,0,0,,But after we finished the oath,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:36.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I found out what it really means\Nto become an "Eternal Girl."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:39.16,Main,,0,0,0,,My wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:41.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Now it gets granted to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:50.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[door opens]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.27,0:19:04.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I made this\Ndrawing in pre-school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:07.02,Main,,0,0,0,,The princess is\Nsupposed to be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.11,0:19:10.28,Main,,0,0,0,,And this black scribble,\Nyou wanna guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:13.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:16.78,Main,,0,0,0,,It's supposed to be\Nof you as my prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.87,0:19:20.16,Main,,0,0,0,,This drawing is of us\Non our wedding day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:23.70,Main,,0,0,0,,But the other kids told\Nme it was dirty and wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.79,0:19:25.37,Main,,0,0,0,,So I did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:28.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Scribbled over it,\Ntried to cover it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:32.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:33.59,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:35.38,Main,,0,0,0,,It was still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:39.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:43.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Try as I might, these\Nfeelings won't go away, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:49.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:51.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:53.98,Main,,0,0,0,,And in the same way you love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:55.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:19:58.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I've felt this\Nway a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.45,0:19:59.78,Main,,0,0,0,,but because we're family,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:02.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I kept those feelings\Nto myself just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.83,0:20:05.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I did my best\Nto block them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:08.42,Main,,0,0,0,,But to hell with that,\NI can't do it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:10.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:11.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:13.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't care what people think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.13,0:20:14.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Or what they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:17.09,Main,,0,0,0,,If it means I have to give up\Nanything and everything
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.17,0:20:19.43,Main,,0,0,0,,to be with you, so be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:21.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I love you, Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.43,0:20:22.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.60,0:20:24.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I swear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.98,0:20:29.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO (Y)]\NI love you, too, Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:30.94,Main,,0,0,0,,So very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:36.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO (Y)] I'm so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:38.95,Main,,0,0,0,,The wish has\Nfinally come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:44.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] So not just your life...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:48.46,Main,,0,0,0,,she took your wish\Nall for herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:55.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[VOICE]\NAnd now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.01,0:20:57.76,Main,,0,0,0,,You become an LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:05.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.73,0:21:09.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE sobs softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:15.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Once the\NSelector is replaced,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,they become\Nanother person's LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:26.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:27.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.83,0:21:29.96,Main,,0,0,0,,...Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.04,0:21:31.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NSo whether we win or lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:35.67,Main,,0,0,0,,it's the Selectors who suffer,\Nand the LRIGs who benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:37.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe they were fighting\Nto become human again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.67,0:21:39.09,Main,,0,0,0,,all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.18,0:21:44.60,Main,,0,0,0,,And yet, she did\Ngrant my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.68,0:21:47.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Holding up her end of this\Nperverse contract, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:49.60,Main,,0,0,0,,And I became an Eternal Girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.68,0:21:52.23,Main,,0,0,0,,To repeat the cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.31,0:21:54.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Get it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.19,0:21:56.40,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the ugly truth\Nbehind this game!
